# Required for production (Vercel): frontend and backend live on separate
# hosts (Vercel + SmarterASP.NET), so there's no dev-server proxy to fall
# back on. Set this in Vercel's dashboard under Settings > Environment
# Variables, not in a committed .env file. Leave unset for local dev — the
# Vite dev server proxy in vite.config.ts handles it there instead.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://yoursite.smarterasp.net
